location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

properties.Description: OpenShiftClusterProperties represents an OpenShift cluster's properties.

servicePrincipalProfile.Description: ServicePrincipalProfile represents a service principal profile.

apiserverProfile.Description: APIServerProfile represents an API server profile.

pullSecret.Description: The pull secret for the cluster (immutable).

resourceGroupId.Description: The ID of the cluster resource group (immutable).

url.Description: The URL to access the cluster console (immutable).

clientId.Description: The client ID used for the cluster (immutable).

clientSecret.Description: The client secret used for the cluster (immutable).

podCidr.Description: The CIDR used for OpenShift/Kubernetes Pods (immutable).

serviceCidr.Description: The CIDR used for OpenShift/Kubernetes Services (immutable).

vmSize.Description: The size of the master VMs (immutable).

subnetId.Description: The Azure resource ID of the master subnet (immutable).

name.Description: The worker profile name.  Must be "worker" (immutable).

vmSize.Description: The size of the worker VMs (immutable).

diskSizeGB.Description: The disk size of the worker VMs.  Must be 128 or greater (immutable).

subnetId.Description: The Azure resource ID of the worker subnet (immutable).

count.Description: The number of worker VMs.  Must be between 3 and 20 (immutable).

url.Description: The URL to access the cluster API server (immutable).

ip.Description: The IP of the cluster API server (immutable).

name.Description: The ingress profile name.  Must be "default" (immutable).
